parameters:
Countless eons have passed, waiting for the day
when someone with true power is reincarnated...

\C[21] I can entrust it to you... You will become
a magical girl and be reborn in a new world...

......Ah... That's right... I... In order to save
someone... I'm sure it's inside the book...

Reincarnation? I don't really know, but it feels
like I have some important role... Ahh... When I
try to remember... my head hurts...!

It goes against reason to carry over memories as
they are. However, if it's fragments of
memories...

In the world I was reincarnated into, I should be
able to gradually recover my memories.
Konoha, I have a favor to ask.
Please save me from the crisis of \C[21]...

\C[21]Now, the world is on the verge of
destruction at the hands of a certain individual.
I will do whatever it takes to prevent that.
I can only rely on you for that.

Once I am reincarnated, I won't be able to
interfere with you anymore.
You are the only one I can rely on...
Who are you? Why is my sword changing?

Well, if that's the case, I guess there's no other
choice...

I don't know what has happened to that world, but
I will do whatever I can to try and make a
difference.

It would be troublesome if my memories don't come
back...

Thank you very much... Well then, I will prepare
for reincarnation...
What?! My body has become smaller!

...Something troublesome is happening right away
in my new reincarnation... I will slightly adjust
the original coordinates of my intended
reincarnation destination.

What?! I don't understand! Can I really fight like
this?!

\C[21] Well then... Please... I hope you...
receive the blessings of Breia Node...
